!!!
%html
  %head
    %title PeriodicCalculationsDemo
    %meta{:content => "width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0", :name => "viewport"}
      = stylesheet_link_tag    "application", media: "all", "data-turbolinks-track" => true
      = javascript_include_tag "application", "data-turbolinks-track" => true
      = csrf_meta_tags
  %body
    .container
      .header
        %ul.nav.nav-pills.pull-right
          %li{ class: menu_class('demo') }
            %a{:href => root_path } Demo
          %li{ class: menu_class('data') }
            %a{:href => purchases_path } Data

        %h3.text-muted Periodic Calculations Demo
        %p
          Periodic Calculations gem allows you to retrieve <b>periodic results of aggregates that can be accumulated over time</b> with PostgreSQL.
        %p
          This examples shows how easy it is to retrieve stats using different metrics, aggregates and windows can be used to retrieve the statistics.
          %br
          It uses window functions and allows you to avoid using precomputed tables that need to be recurringly updated.
